title: Ethereum Holesky testnet launch flops, relaunch is expected in coming weeks
description:
Ethereum’s Holesky testnet experienced an error that will require another launch attempt, community members and developers said on Sept. 15. Ethereum researcher Diederik Loerakker, aka protolambda, wrote that one developer entered certain data in the wrong part of the network’s genesis files. He said: “Someone put 0x686f77206d7563682069732074686520666973683f (“how much is the fish?”) as extra-data in […]
